de.hs_duesseldorf.medien.mi.httphsdronelog.hsdronelog.network.util.json

Interface JSONReaderListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JSONRequestParser

    public interface JSONReaderListener
    This interface listens to a JSONReader while parsing. If the JSONReader reads a new JSON statement it will call the method which belongs to the event / statement.
